messages.content: 9-1-1, what's your emergency?
Hi, there's gunshots. We're all on the floor.
They've been gunshots? We're all on the floor.
We're over on Arlington University right next to Walgreens. We're on 5551, Arlington Road.
Has anybody been shot?
I don't know. We're all inside. We all came inside.
Do you hear anyone screaming out like they've been shot? Or did you see the vehicle that did the shooting?
There are people screaming outside. A lot of people screaming outside.
Did you see them actually shoot the weapon or you just heard the shot?
We all heard the shots and all came right inside. Everyone I hear that's in the building is not hurt. No one's hurt.
Is this in a building, like apartments or a residence?
We're in a building across from Walgreens. Called Midnight Expresso.
The cops are already here.
Okay, thank you.
You're welcome. Bye-bye.
There are gunshots going off on Arlington Road and University Boulevard. I don't know if anyone's been shot.
How many shots did you hear?
About five, six, seven.
Did you hear any cars speeding off?
No.
Okay, sir, what's your last name?
Christopher Lemlin, L-E-M-E-L-I-N.
I'll get an officer out there and let them know.
Okay, they might want to send an ambulance.
Okay, they're on their way.
Jacksonville 911, what's your emergency?
I'm calling to report gunshots.
Did you see anybody get shot, ma'am?
No, but I hear people outside screaming now.
Where at? Is this at a house, apartment, or mobile home?
Mine is a house.
How many shots did you hear?
Maybe five, but I didn't see who shot the individual. I was almost asleep.
We've gotten other calls that someone was shot. What is your last name, ma'am?
Johnson.
Okay, ma'am, we have officers on the way. Thank you.
Thanks.
Bye-bye.
9-1-1, what's your emergency?
I'm like one block away from the corner of University Boulevard and Arlington Road. I heard like four or five shots, and now I hear a lot of people screaming on the corner.
Ma'am, we are responding to a shooting over there. Where are you located?
I'm at the next street behind University, called Easter Street. I know something bad's happening up there.
We have officers on the way. Thank you, ma'am.
No problem. What's your last name?
Jacksonville 9-1-1, what's your emergency?
There was a gunfight going on University Boulevard by Walgreens.
Do you see the people involved?
No, but I see people running down the street.
How many did you see run off?
Three.
Could you tell what they had on?
No, it's dark. I couldn't tell.
I'll let them know they ran down Macy Avenue. What's your last name?
Jacksonville 9-1-1, what's your emergency?
Hello, there's been a shooting down the street at Club Minnow's.
Where at, sir? What's the address?
On University, down the street from Walgreens.
Did you see anybody get shot?
No, I just heard gunshots, letting y'all know.
We have officers out in the area.
Okay, thank you.
You're welcome.
